  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5009654">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5009654/" class="title-link">通往亚里士多德的这条路</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5009654"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36771726-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">唐山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-07-03"
      class="main-meta">2011-07-03 11:26:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5009654_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  人类为什么要善？它源于不可言说的使命，还是理性？  在中国的传统文化认识中，善是人性的核心组成部分，不证自明，因为通过直觉能够感受到它：行善有快感，行恶有痛感。每个人天然爱自己的孩子，天然尊敬自己的父母，这种恻隐之心推而广之，则世界大同，所以古人很少追问善是...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5009654/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5009654_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5009654_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
